    {
        "content": "<p>Using <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=Filter.nonempty_of_mem#doc\">docs#Filter.nonempty_of_mem</a> you get <code>N.Nonempty</code>, which you can destruct into an element in <code>N</code>. Then you can just apply <code>h</code> to this element.</p>",
